title: Manchester United star Michael Carrick could be in line for a shock move to Arsenal as Arsene Wenger looks to bolster his midfield
text:
EFL EMIRATES CALLING Manchester United star Michael Carrick could be in line for a shock move to Arsenal as Arsene Wenger looks to bolster his midfield 
The England midfielder becomes a free agent in the summer and could be in line for a return to North London, having previously played for Tottenham Hotspur Exclusive
